{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was coming everyday to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were talking very-- not political, but very openly about things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when, later, came the amnesty for us, when the war-- when Sikorsky was in Moscow and signed the pact with Stalin, as a matter of fact, I found out about the amnesty-- one day, I was in the tent and came a Russian general, a Jew, was an old Chekist from Dzerzhinsky's days.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I first time saw him and he said to me, do you want to go to fight with Mr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sikorsky.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't understand-- he said there's a amnesty for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are going to join the Polish army under Russian command and you will fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, really, we were called in two days later, and put into trucks and sent back to the harbor place, the harbor on the White Sea.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we were brought to the trucks, I was put in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was about 700 of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was put in charge of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the political officer came to me and said to me, look, you will soon maybe leave Russia and you will have bad memories about Russia because you were not treated very well.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, look, when we will have this bad memories and be critical of everything, try to be non-- not partial, and think about the good sides, as well.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Think about the education we gave to people, think about the medical system, which didn't exist, we gave to people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not everything was wrong here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And do you know, any time I talk about Russia now, this words come to me back?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, I was in charge of this group of 700.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't know where the Polish army is forming.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
